Global Luxury Multi Passenger Stroller Market Insights
Luxury Multi Passenger Stroller Market market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 3.0 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Luxury Multi Passenger Stroller Market Overview
The global luxury multi-passenger stroller market is witnessing significant growth due to the increasing demand for premium, comfortable, and high-quality strollers for families with multiple children. The market size reached USD 1.24 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030. This expansion is driven by the rising preference for convenience, the growing number of dual-income households, and the increasing trend of outdoor activities, fostering demand for high-end strollers that offer both style and functionality. Moreover, technological advancements, such as lightweight frames, improved suspension systems, and enhanced safety features, have also contributed to market growth.

